			Company Description 


			Sinopec Kantons Holdings Ltd. is an investment holding company with interests in providing logistics and trading services. The company operates its business through four segments: Trading of Crude Oil, Crude Oil Jetty Services, Natural Gas Pipeline Transmission Services and Vessel Charter Services. ...
		


                Sinopec Kantons Holdings Ltd. is an investment holding company with interests in providing logistics and trading services. The company operates its business through four segments: Trading of Crude Oil, Crude Oil Jetty Services, Natural Gas Pipeline Transmission Services and Vessel Charter Services. The Trading of Crude Oil segment trades crude oil in Hong Kong and China. The Crude Oil Jetty Services segment provides crude oil transportation, unloading, storage, and other jetty services for oil tankers. The Natural Gas Pipeline Transmission Services Segment provides transmission services through its natural gas pipelines located in the PRC. The Vessel Charter Services segment provides vessel chartering for crude oil transportation and floating oil storage facilities for oil tankers. Sinopec Kantons Holdings was founded in March 1998 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.
            




